<title>gẖyrt ḥyạty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (gẖyrt ḥyạty .. bḥb ʿjyb
 wmʿạk fy smạk .. bqy̱ lyã nṣyb)2
 1- ạ̹kẖtrt tyjyny .. wạnạ wsṭ ậnyny
 mdyt ly ạ̹ydyk ạlḥlwẗ .. wʿynyk tsbyny
 nsytny ậlạmy .. rjʿt slạmy
 wạdytny frḥẗ wbhjẗ .. (wmsẖyt qdạmy)2
 2- wbḍʿfy hạjy lk .. yạ yswʿ wạnạdy lk
 tgẖslny bqwẗ dmk .. yrfʿny ṣlybk
 tsẖfy ly jrwḥy .. wtbdl nwḥy
 bsʿạdẗ wnṣrẗ fy sẖkẖṣk .. (tnʿsẖ ly rwḥy)2
 3- ạ̉yạmy ạljạyẗ .. fy ạ̹ydyk mḥmyẗ
 msẖ kẖạyf ʿ ạlmstqbl .. ʿsẖạn ạ̹nt rạʿyã
 wạtẖq fy wʿwdk .. mlạzmny wjwdk
 wḥyạty ạ̹nt gẖạmrhạ .. (bạlkẖyr mn jwdk)2</lyrics>
